    <item>
      <title>顶级经济学家称中国已准备好迎接 1.4 万亿美元的财政刺激计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/china-economist-suggests-1-4-trillion-bond-sale-in-stimulus-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国一位著名经济学家表示，中国有空间通过发行高达 10 万亿元人民币（1.4 万亿美元）的特别债务来加大对经济的财政支持，这反映出人们对北京将扩大公共支出作为刺激计划一部分的预期日益高涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/china-economist-suggests-1-4-trillion-bond-sale-in-stimulus-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 05:06:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油期权显示市场有望因中东战争进一步上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/oil-options-shows-market-sees-further-gains-on-middle-east-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[期权显示，投资者押注油价将进一步上涨，因为以色列和伊朗之间不断升级的敌对行动有可能损害中东的能源基础设施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/oil-options-shows-market-sees-further-gains-on-middle-east-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 02:01:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东紧张局势加剧，股市下跌，油价上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中东冲突升级的风险削弱了市场风险偏好，导致欧洲股市与美国股指期货一同下跌。经济数据可能为美联储的政策走向提供更多指引，在此之前，市场风险偏好有所减弱。原油延续涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 22:36:35 GMT</pubDate>
